metadata.name: McIntosh White #1/10
metadata.description:
Taken in London, February 2018.

Artist: Craig Reilly

Edition: 1/10

A limited edition of 10 copies of this photo was made in order to commemorate one year in web3. 

In conjunction with the CR46 editions series, each collector who owns all three images from the primary market will receive an edition of 'McIntosh White' free.

License Agreement: This image can be displayed privately, as well as in commercial and non-commercial settings, and/or in groups with an unlimited number of participants.

This license includes unlimited use and display in physical or virtual galleries, documentaries, and essays by the NFT holder. This license provides no rights to create commercial merchandise, commercial distribution, or derivative works.
